Philip Winchester https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_Winchester 0 Philip C. Winchester (born March 24, 1981) is an English-American actor. He is known for his roles in The Patriot, The Hi-Line, LD 50 Lethal Dose, Thunderbirds, CSI: Miami, King Lear, Strike Back, Flyboys, In My Sleep, The Heart of the Earth and Shaking Dream Land. He is mostly known for his role as Peter Stone in Chicago Justice and Law Order: Special Victims Unit. Philip_C._Winchester ( born March_24 , 1981 ) is an_English-American_actor .
